<body>

<h1>power off/on</h1>
<p>this section will run the app. this is actually the main button that is used as the app icon</p>

<h1>pick a nearby user</h1>
<p>upon activation the app will activate its gps to find other users within 1, 5, 10, 25 or 50 miles</p>
<p> the user will see the other nearby, active users in a list of links</p>
<p> when a user link is chosen the msg screen will appear that is dedicated to that individual</p>

<h1>send him/her a message</h1>
<p>now the fun part. the user will type a message to the recipient</p>
<p>then the app will alert the recipient, keeping the new message on hold until it is read</p>
<p> when the recipient opens the message the timer starts</p>
<p> when the 30 second timer elapses the message is erased from the recipient app (it is automatically erased from the sender app as soon as he/she pushes send</p>


